node.text: Here’s the process💨 40ft long 🗿 6ft tall & around 15,000 pounds of stone! It’s crafted from dry stone and it took 2 months to build. It was my first time ever working with stone so it was a wild puzzle ✨ Stoked to build something new for my family so they can enjoy the backyard views 🙌🏼 #DIY #stonewalls #backyardproject #arch #architecture
